metadata.name: cassandra
metadata.description:
We present one of Viscerina's final artworks titled "cassandra". As a homage to Viscerina, this artwork serves as a celebration of her incredible talent and a poignant reminder of her passing. All proceeds generated from this will be directed towards her medical and memorial expenses, ensuring that her legacy will live on in our Ghost Club collection and in the hearts of those who loved her.

Midjourney / 27" x 27" / 4096x4096 / jpg
